high_descs: go to the sidetable in the living room.
get the butterknife from top of the coffee table.
take the desklamp back with you to the bedroom.
Turn on the desklamp using the stick.
anns.task_desc: Use ButterKnife to turn on DeskLamp in another room.

high_descs: Take a left and leave the room and go towards the sidetable.
Pick up the butterknife on the table.
Turn left and go back to the desklamp in the bedroom.
Go to the desklamp and turn on the desklamp.
anns.task_desc: Pick up the ButterKnife on the coffee table and then go into the room and turn on the DeskLamp.

high_descs: Head across the room and turn left to reach the side table.
Pick up the butter knife from the side table.
Turn around and turn right and head to the desk lamp in the room.
anns.task_desc: Examine the butter knife under the lamp light.
